工激活星形胶质细胞时，鱼立即停下来。这表明星形胶质细胞积极介导从希望到绝望的转变。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/once-thought-to-support-neurons-astrocytes-turn-out-to-be-in-charge.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 01:18:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/once-thought-to-support-neurons-astrocytes-turn-out-to-be-in-charge</guid></item><item><title>昆虫唾液效应器破坏以 PIEZO1 为中心的针对刺吸载体的机械免疫</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/insect-salivary-effectors-disrupt-piezo1-centric-mechanoimmunity-against-piercing-sucking-vectors</link><description>黄等人。识别机械敏感通道&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/insect-salivary-effectors-disrupt-piezo1-centric-mechanoimmunity-against-piercing-sucking-vectors2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 01:03:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/insect-salivary-effectors-disrupt-piezo1-centric-mechanoimmunity-against-piercing-sucking-vectors</guid></item><item><title>产妇缺血性中风后的长期恢复、发病率和死亡率</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/long-term-recovery-morbidity-and-mortality-after-maternal-ischemic-stroke</link><description>本研究研究了产妇缺血性中风后的长期恢复、发病率和死亡率。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/long-term-recovery-morbidity-and-mortality-after-maternal-ischemic-stroke2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 00:48:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/long-term-recovery-morbidity-and-mortality-after-maternal-ischemic-stroke</guid></item><item><title>血液特征可更好地预测 2 型糖尿病风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/01/signature-in-blood-to-better-predict-type-2-diabetes-risk</link><description>还发现与 2 型糖尿病相关的代谢物与该疾病相关的临床特征和组织类型存在遗传关联。此外，该团队还开发了 44 种代谢物的独特特征，可以改善对未来 2 型糖尿病风险的预测。科学任务科学新闻亮点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/signature-in-blood-to-better-predict-type-2-diabetes-risk2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2026 00:33:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blo